                        Add comfort to your journey by traveling through our luxury and gold class buses. All buses are equipped with:
                        <ul>

                            <li> • Comfortable and spacious seats.</li>
                            <li> • Latest audio visual technologies.</li>
                            <li> • Apart from this, a calm and peaceful environment is maintained in the bus for a luxurious traveling.</li>
                            

                        </ul>

                    </p>
