                    <p>
                        Every possible support is available for carrying personal luggage while traveling. Please be aware that depending on local regulations, certain items which may cause injuries may not be taken on board in your carry-on baggage. Following are some available facilities:

                        <ul>

                            <li> • Luggage up to 30 KG can be carried by each passenger .</li>
                            <li> • In case of extra luggage, Extra Luggage (ELT) facility can be availed.</li>
                            <li> • Attachment of luggage tags for safety and security.</li>
                            <li> • Luggage is handled by trained loaders.</li>
                            <li> • Porters providing free of cost service.</li>

                        </ul>

                    </p>
